text: Earpod or ear pod or variant may refer to: * Apple EarPods earphones introduced with iPhone 5; see Apple earbuds * Acacia auriculiformis, the earpod or earpod wattle a tree from Australasia * Enterolobium contortisiliquum, the earpod or Pacara earpod a tree * Enterolobium cyclocarpum, the earpod a tree
title: Earpod
